Boundary Manipulations
----------------------

Directions:	move boundary by 1 unit in corresponding 
		direction.

r		toggle placement search type between by-row and 
		by-column

v		toggle vertical placement direction between 
		top-to-bottom and bottom-to-top.

t		set vertical placement to top-to-bottom.

b		set vertical placement to bottom-to-top.

h		toggle horizontal placement direction between 
		left-to-right and right-to-left.

x		toggle between process and ignore events.

m		toggle between play and block events.

